def s(n):
   for i in range(n, 0, -1):
       if n%i == 0:
           return i

def main():
    n = int(input())
    t = input()
    d = s(n)
    print(t[d:], end=" ")
    print(t[:d][::-1], end=" ")

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
